data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the beautiful city of St. Cloud! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem offers not only a functional layout but also a plethora of amenities that will have you falling in love at first sight.    Step inside and be captivated by the open concept design, creating the perfect space for entertaining family and friends. The spacious living area seamlessly flows into the dining room and kitchen, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere that will make every gathering unforgettable.    Need a quiet space to get some work done or immerse yourself in your favorite hobbies? Look no further than the office/den, a versatile room that can be transformed to suit your needs - the possibilities are simply endless!    As if the interior wasn't enticing enough, this community truly has it all. Enjoy lazy summer days lounging by the shimmering community pool, perfect for beating the Florida heat. Take advantage of the community playground that promises endless laughter and adventure for your little ones, creating cherished memories that will last a lifetime.    To top it all off, indulge in the serene pond view, offering a picturesque backdrop to relax and unwind after a long day. Imagine sipping your morning coffee on the patio, basking in the tranquility and beauty that nature has to offer.    With its convenient location in the heart of St. Cloud, you'll have easy access to a variety of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Commuting will be a breeze thanks to the nearby highways, putting all of Central Florida's attractions within reach.    Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to call this house your home. Come and see it for yourself - you won't be disappointed! Contact us today to book your private showing and start envisioning the incredible memories that await you in your new dream home.
